        <h2>Vision & Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
            This engineering platform is built around the objective of improving
            energy efficiency and enhancing the performance of thermal and energy systems.
            It promotes a systematic and analytical approach to understanding,
            optimizing and modernizing existing energy infrastructures.
        </p>
